{
  "stem": "24830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ask my mother to let me use one room, that I make like a little studio to-- to paint and draw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How old were you then when you-- when you did that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, 16, about, 17.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This part is not very clear, you know, because I didn't think about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't tell me you were going to ask me, [LAUGHS] so I didn't think about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what I remember is every room has a fireplace, which is nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we have-- oh, and the kitchen was-- well, in the-- yeah, across the-- you have the stair, and across were all the-- the material was-- you know, wool and silk.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had everything there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, we use is as a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For-- for-- for France, it was a big-- big place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know because during the war, you have to-- to light the, you know, the fire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bring-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know-- [FRENCH], and light the fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, every room had a fireplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I guess most place must have been like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always like fireplaces.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, you know, the war started in '39, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The declaration of war with France started in 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nothing happened for a whole year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were living normally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was no change in your life at all--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No. --during that period?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we had no change because we-- we never dreamed that the German will, you know, will-- will come to France.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I think in 19-- I forget when the German came to Paris.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have the date.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I have the-- anyway, when the German came to Paris, everything was still normal for almost a year.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
